bb_tag\" ><strong>SOUND & MUSIC</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breakbeat, Jungle, DnB all in the style of the early 2000’s </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound effects created with reverence to Source era with extra raw oomph  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of fun references for those who pay attention to sounds effects in games  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMMUNITY</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finnish solo developer with a passionate community  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Discord for feedback, feature testing, devlogs and sneak peeks for upcoming content  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m very open to feedback so this is a great time to get your voice heard!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509160/extras/6c12a721ec509f8e873b579879d26103.poster.avif?t=1760021823\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509160/extras/6c12a721ec509f8e873b579879d26103.webm?t=1760021823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3509160/extras/6c12a721ec509f8e873b579879d26103.mp4?t=1760021823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
